description:
Danny welcomes Andy Cohen's assistant Daryn Carp (Host of Martini's & Murder/Bravo's Weekly Pregame) to talk ALL things Bravo. They run through the rumor mill, discuss iconic Housewives moments, the future of Flipping Out, Southern Charm, potential new Housewives franchises, and SO much more.


Daryn: 2:26ish
